<li id="cite_note-MPC-7">^ <a href="#cite_ref-MPC_7-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-MPC_7-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="/wiki/Frank_Schmalleger" title="Frank Schmalleger">Frank Schmalleger</a>, <i>Criminal Law Today: An Introduction with Capstone Cases," p. 115, N. 29, citing <a href="/wiki/Model_Penal_Code" title="Model Penal Code">Model Penal Code</a>, § 5.01 (2).</i></li>
<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class=""><i>Ng Chun Pui v. Li Chuen Tat</i>, RTR, 1988</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Ng+Chun+Pui+v.+Li+Chuen+Tat&amp;rft.date=1988&amp;rft.place=RTR&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Res_ipsa_loquitur"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class=""><i>Gee v. Metropolitan Ry</i>, 1873</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Gee+v.+Metropolitan+Ry&amp;rft.date=1873&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Res_ipsa_loquitur"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class=""><i>Barkway v. South Wales Transport</i>, 1 All ER, 1950</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Barkway+v.+South+Wales+Transport&amp;rft.date=1950&amp;rft.place=1+All+ER&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Res_ipsa_loquitur"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class=""><i>=Scott v. London &amp; Catherine Dock Co 3 H&amp;C 596</i>, 1865</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=%3DScott+v.+London+%26+Catherine+Dock+Co+3+H%26C+596&amp;rft.date=1865&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Res_ipsa_loquitur"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class=""><i>McDyer v. Celtic Football Club</i>, SC, 2000</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=McDyer+v.+Celtic+Football+Club&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.place=SC&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Res_ipsa_loquitur"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class=""><i>McQueen v The Glasgow Garden Festival 1988 Ltd</i>, SLT</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=McQueen+v+The+Glasgow+Garden+Festival+1988+Ltd&amp;rft.place=SLT&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Res_ipsa_loquitur"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
</div>
